      <t>This memo defines the Initial Entries for the Performance Metrics
   Registry.  This version includes:

   * Revised several Poisson streams to Periodic, sections 4 &amp; 5.

   * Addition of ICMP (ping) metrics in section 9.

   * First implementation of Passive TCP RTT metrics in section 10.

   Still need: Add MBM metric entry.</t>
